[{"index":1,"title":"【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"女孩问男孩答，女孩说一下自己的看法，男孩说一下自己的看法吧，拜&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;午后，慵懒的阳光洒落地面，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>纵长路上，男孩骑车载着女孩.....&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>[你会爱我多久？]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩紧抱着男孩，侧着头在他耳边这样甜甜的问，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>她知道，这个问题没有100分的答案。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>带着娇嗔的轻笑，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>她说：「给你一个说甜言蜜语的机会。」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>男孩却认真的思考了起来。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>趁着红灯停止的机会，他举起手比了个“一”&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>要女孩猜猜他的答案是什麽。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩想了一想，快乐的说：「一辈子！」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>男孩笑了，并不是因为她答对，而是感染了她的喜悦。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>绿灯了，男孩不仅趋车面对现实，也收敛起笑容，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>轻轻的告诉女孩：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「我不会给这种答案的，这样的答案好到不真实了，像在说谎..再猜猜..」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩对男孩的说法很满意，於是歪者头继续想..&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「一天？」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「呵呵，我们已经相恋两个月了，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>一天、一星期、一个月这些都不成立喔！」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>又是红灯，男孩握住女孩的手，微笑的看着她，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩窃笑，大声的说「不会是一瞬间吧？」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>这个答案让男孩差点笑倒在马路上「当然不是啦！」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>他一直深爱着女孩的幽默，深爱着女孩爽朗的笑容，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>这个答案让他更紧握住女孩的手....&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「一年吗？」曾经有过一年时间等待的承诺，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>使得女孩对一年这个答案特别敏感。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>男孩摇摇头，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>他们之间已经不需要等待，只剩时间的考验.......&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「一百年好了，爱我一百年就够了。」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩说着，并表现着幸福的模样。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>男孩说「一百年太短了吧，不够我爱你啊！」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>甜言蜜语是男孩的专长，爱听甜言蜜语却是女孩的弱点....&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩笑了，轻铃的笑声让男孩闯了红灯....&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「想要听答案了吗？」男孩想说了，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>而女孩想听「我会爱你多久呢？」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>男孩手比着一说：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>「一.......一直到你不再爱我的那一天.......」&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>女孩怔了……&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>一直到你不再爱我的那一天......&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>回帖你的爱人会象他一样爱你&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>不回就会变成没人爱没人疼的可怜虫&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\u0018","author":"清水§芙蓉","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9f2b0776.vDOQfGBzyUlyWcL_1rdZPg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:27","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"看过的~~很感动的说`�","author":"雪￡魅儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec7c4b5f.KSJNpCIUJLOmFrJ1VJmBpQ&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"呵~我在没看答案之前就猜出来�","author":"风铃≌摇摇","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.cfd1d03e.AMqAx4yImfXPR1yUv18nEg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:39","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"?","author":"雪￡魅儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec7c4b5f.KSJNpCIUJLOmFrJ1VJmBpQ&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-08 19:51","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"恩..............很感动的撒~~~~~~~~~~~","author":"哔哔A","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2c7116ad.mJsXB4OlGaQEBs4HVdLtXA&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-09 10:08","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"恩，很富哲理的说......","author":"漩涡素娜","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c4bcea1e.Z1TNwE4eflfdr3Ksex4WuA&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-09 10:15","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：【感动】女孩问男孩答","content":"哪个谁？爱我啊？","author":"南宫雨彦","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5464c1e2.JxCJyH499HmKYB6nKvBxqA&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-10 20:42","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,